(4) Any contribution payable by the associated authorities under the provisions of subsection (2) shall be contributed by such authorities in proportion to the contributions paid by each such authority in respect of the current service of members during the financial year in respect of which such contribution is payable. [As amended by Act No. 14 of 1990 ]
